durang: 1~Nedar Burujolare Siṛimi ci Siruṅ.~Ginataególaya ॥koṅ॥~Kana ṉhapui Siṛimi, kanah ṉhapui Siruṅ,~Baleć misińtańe Cana ginataególoya ॥koṅ॥²
2~Sasaṅakan Piḍingire, sunumakan Piḍingire.~Baleć mising tańe cana kitaṕ saṭao tan ॥koṅ॥~Ṉocare Dikuṉhon, Ṉhora ṉaṅkirvaićmea.~Misińere murukuṅ nelsenoḱtea ॥koṅ॥²
3~Kákasakam tinjarbonjar,~Cekan kilitana jam dinḍaṉhapanum ॥koṅ॥²~Kili kam jagar redo,~Nańaḱ kili ² teń kili misame ॥koṅ॥²

4~Nhesaḱ mata matalena baḍi mata matalena (ṭik samay rege~Tuyum seṭer akana) ॥koṅ॥²~Nhesaḱ mata ² caba jana baḍi mata ² caba jana~Sama gea tuyum bonḍo l akana ॥koṅ॥²~Ṉale noṛaāre tuyu seta menaḱć(hakaka bakaka tana~Tuyu kakiṛi mea) ॥koṅ॥²
5~Misiń Raca Bakara kiṭuṕakan tiruṕakana ॥koṅ॥²~Ṭapaṭapa Baduṛi, ṭapa gasarket́ ॥koṅ॥²
6~Nimiṅ Jeṭe nimiṅ Lolo~Nen Ṉulisakamdona kana gasaroḱ ॥koṅ॥~Baleć Kimiń seṭerlena,~Nen Ṉulisakamdona kana gasaroḱ ॥koṅ॥
7~Latarayte Jugiṉhon, cetanayte Jugiṉhon.~Koekoete Jugim seṭerlena ॥koṅ॥²~Ṉengań goṛe menaḱćreca,~Ṉapuń goṛe menaḱćreca,~ 'koye, koyedo jugi nonah koyado noma meh ॥koṅ॥²

8~Daḱ do daḱ do tetaṅhi tan,~Lai do lai do rengehi tana.~Nokon kore dudulum daḱ do beṭaoha ॥koṅ॥~Cimin saning cimin jiliṅ,~Nokon reja dudulum daḱ do beṭaoha ॥koṅ॥~Daṅh do beṭao hametam,~Diri sut́, rugut́ sut́ dah do beṭaoha ॥koṅ॥²
9~Munḍa ko Racare, santa ko Racare,~Kuṭura ci muta riṛi hekena ॥koṅ॥²~Kana ṉhapui kuṭura, akana nhapui muta,~Munḍa kore talaṕ ṭaka riḍiṅ hekena ॥koṅ॥²
10~Buru bitar Mage, beḍa bitar Mage,~Cekatere Daṛacuń ṉaiumelet́a ॥koṅ॥²~Rutu riu ² teń ṉayum mele ḍah ॥koṅ॥~Banam ceo ² teń ṉayum mele ḍah॥
11~Neder Piṛi ² t akan sari baṅ, kalai ba nerainelaḍah ॥koṅ॥²~Gonoṅsati menaḱ recalaṅ keā ruāi॥
12~Ṉaben dona baleć Bareń,~Rutu tedo, banam tedo nesum rasika ॥koṅ॥²~Rutu te do banam te kaben Ṉasuloḱ ॥koṅ॥
13~Ṉengań, nhapui menaḱ redo,~Baṛi daru lidi ² sua riṅ ॥koṅ॥²~Nengay, nhapui bangay,~Baṛi daru lidi ², doṛa he jana ॥koṅ॥²
14~Ṉabendoja baleć Bareń,~Kenjar bonjar raja doben beṭa taya ci ॥koṅ॥²~Beṭa ṛoliṅ beṭa taya,~Samaṛam ganḍu rinki rakaṕ akana ॥koṅ॥²
15~Buru mage cabahana, beṛa mage caba hana,~Cigo cekan teben tolgoćena ॥koṅ॥²~Niha tinge sanaṅh,~Baṭa baṭi burure baṭi gojen ben ॥koṅ॥²
16~Nender buru jolare,~Jiki cina, sarasanḍi manḍa rakab let́a ॥koṅ॥~Kana nhapui jiki, akana nhapui sarasanḍi,~Baleć Bareńh ca metam manḍa rakaṕ leṛa ॥koṅ॥
17~Cia cia cepar Hon, cia cia guturahona.~Haga ko disu meh do bugitana cia ॥koṅ॥~Sukuge bano, dukuge~Maḍako bir kore ko bakaṛatana ॥koṅ॥²

18~Ṉabendoja baleć Bareń, Burubitar Reaṛi benaniro niriya,~ṉhoromataleeredo, jangimataleeredo,~Magereaḱ Dotidoben kirĩya ci ॥koṅ॥²~Kaben kirĩya redo, kaben kejanay redo,~Ṉaben geda balego barey disum tumio ॥koṅ॥
19~Cetan pukari cel copol,~Latar pukari cel cola.~Baṅ lekan naku kiṅ rakaṕe lena ॥koṅ॥²~Jĩbiri menahḱ reca laṅ, jibiri koṭouṅ kiṅ ॥koṅ॥²~Raba menaḱ reca laṅ, raba koṭouṅ kiṅ ॥koṅ॥²
20~Bareń Raca kadam daru,~Sankodaru cetanete Daḱdo jorotana ॥koṅ॥²~Daḱ do telae ben Bareń,~Sona rupa tiṛite da, do telae ben ॥koṅ॥²
21~Jiṛim suku jan redo;~Boṛo reā Baha Nhapanum Baha nemańe meh ॥koṅ॥²~Jiṛi karem suku jan redo,~Boṛo reā Baha Nhapanum ṉalom nemaṅiaṅ ॥koṅ॥²
22~Cetano ko mag akana, lataro ko mag akana,~Nokonare juṛilang mage misana ॥koṅ॥²~Mage misana lang juṛiṅ,~Bala saka nature lang mage misana ॥koṅ॥²
23~Munḍa ko Raca kadam daru,~Jeṭe tici lolate moyalantana ॥koṅ॥²~Kana nhapui jeṭe te, akana nhapui lolate,~Samay bapui seno tanate, moyalan tan ॥koṅ॥²
24~Disumedo gule gule, raṅnaci do mele mele,~Disum koci Bareń ben niatintana ॥koṅ॥²
25~Ṉaliṅdoja baleć Bareń~Sirima jeṭe, Ṉote lolo riliaṅ ॥koṅ॥²~Ṉabendoja baleć Bareń,~Mat́ko bitar juṅbulae nubul rebena ॥koṅ॥²
26~Cetan pukari, latar pukari,~Maena moh nakukiṅ rakabelena ॥koṅ॥²~Ṉasulikiṅ ben go Bareń,~Bugin ² jagadare Ṉasulikiṅ ben ॥koṅ॥²~Gonoākiṅ ben go Bareń,~Ikoisi baisi kore gonoākiṅ ben ॥koṅ॥²

27~Buru bitar mage do, pata bitar mage do,~Dili kulań ben go Bareń, kaji kulań ben ॥koṅ॥²~Kaben dili kulań redo, kaben kaji kulań redo,~Baṭa baṭi buru reaḱ baṭi gojena ॥koṅ॥~Tole tole buru reṅa tol gojena ॥koṅ॥²
28~Niyang tikiṅ napung tikiṅ menaḱ redo,~Ciṭi kireṅ maḍi, nutu dul akana ॥koṅ॥²~Niyang tikiṅ nhapui tikiṅ bang kiṅā,~Ciṭi kire maḍi nutu noṭang jana ॥koṅ॥²
29~Cetan kunḍi, latar kunḍi~Doneha ci masala leko cenḍo tana~Kana nhapui donea, akana nhapui masala,~Bareń here beneṭa leko cenḍotana ॥koṅ॥²
30~Ṉulicuṭukay riya Bareń~Nisir cenḍo do.~Jagada Daḱ riya Bareń~Keḱ ye baṭa do.~Guli tuṭi menaḱ redo Bareń,~Tuyanja lopoṅ tai mea baleć Bareń ॥koṅ॥²
31~Ṉengańe Ṉapuńe menaḱaredo,~Ṉuliḍumasu ḍumba, kuda ḍumasu ḍumba nuṅbal nerĩāḱ~Negaṅe napuṅe bangaya,~Ṉuliḍumasu ḍumba, kuda ḍumasu ḍumba,~Numbul goyo natu ḍing ॥koṅ॥²
32~Nape disum do munḍa,~Dirisut́ bonj raja dado niji tan ॥koṅ॥²~Ṉale disum do munḍa,~Pataa gasar jan redo dado ranjeḍo ॥koṅ॥²

33~Hatu kuṭi uli daru,~Miat́ge jo len esu sibila.~Mata somay hoao redo, jome samay hoao redo,~Kagajo sakamere ole kulaeṅ bena.~Kam ole kulaeṅ redo, kam dili kulaeṅ redo,~Baṭa baṭi buru reṅ baṭṭi gojena॥~Heleke teke buru reṅ tol gojena ॥koṅ॥
34~Kam toṭ akan reó, kam sangar ken reó,~Laṛata jilum nela rem tabu tabuya.~Nisai sarige cakat́ bano,~Laḍata jilum nela rem tabu tabuya ॥koṅ॥
35~Ṉeaṅ Ṉapuń tae kenare,~Bangali doti caeṅ tega tegaya.~Ṉeaṅ Ṉapuń bage ket́iń,~Sert́ lijaḱ botoć botoć akana ॥koṅ॥
36~Mage Poroṕ hobalena,~Nen reciń nu nuā tehareṅ nu nuā ॥koṅ॥
37~Manḍidoko manḍitana, reberebe,~Ṉilidoko calatana coṭocoṭo,~Ṉicaḱbaha Juḍń do Met́eć jolopi ॥koṅ॥²

38~Buddi netoy-ālaṅ Misiń,~Ciṭi miṭi bangalare buddi netoy ālaṅ.~Buddi ṉetokere Misiń, diri lekan se laṭilaṅ nobor ket́a॥~Jaṭi lekan kagajolaṅ nitir ket́a॥~Buddi ṉetokere Misiń,~Nende nonol punḍi kagajo disum jari ket́ ॥koṅ॥

39~Ṉamdona Bareń negam menai,~Ṉamdona bare napum menai,~Sadae jor balego Bareń, catom numbul rem ॥koṅ॥~Nań dona Bareń ṉengań bangae,~Nań dona Bareń nhapuiṅ bagay,~Sadae jor balego Bareń, jibon jeṭe loloreh ॥koṅ॥~Nańonga ṉengań menaḱć redo, ṉańoga naṅpui menaḱć redo,~Sadae jor balego Bareń jiban catom numbul reh ॥koṅ॥

40~Neṭeḍiṅha tanagoṅm bare, neṭeḍiṅh-tanama.~Miat́ĕge Misim tem neṭeḍiṅh-tana ॥koṅ॥~Cabuṛa tańabenago Bareń cabuṛatań ben,~Gelebar doreare cabuṛatań ben ॥koṅ॥~Capa natũi benago Bareń, capa natuiṅ ben,~Nilabaṛi kagajore capa natuiṅ bena.~Meḍadaham joroy-hago Bareń, meḍadaham joroyaha,~Capa sakam nel kete meḍadaham joroyaha ॥koṅ॥

41~Buddim ṉetotan go Bareń,~Biniwr nisikulre buddim ṉetotana ॥koṅ॥~Ṭibul bil akanago Bareń,~āikorṭ bagaṅlare ṭibul bilakana.~Ṭibul cetan rena Bareń,~Sona reha kagajo bilanakah naha ॥koṅ॥~Buddim ṉetolereṅ Bareń,~Sonareha pĩsilate nomboratuimeha ॥koṅ॥

42~Cetan pukari latar pukari,~Napũi geca roṛa let́ joṛa Ṉuli bah ॥koṅ॥ Dhuḱ si0॥~Baṛay nasitan Bareń,~Nede nende sepeṛet́ bahay nasitan ॥koṅ॥ Siḱ du0॥~Baṛago nemaiḱ ben Bareń,~Tiṛigo cetan biṛiteh bahagoh nemaiben ॥koṅ॥ Siḱ du0॥
43~Surugo sutam dogo Bareń gutuèalaṅ,~Cigo Bareń galaṅalaṅ ॥koṅ॥~Buddim ṉetotanago Bareń,~Kumpani duhare buddim netotana ॥koṅ॥~Nisirakanagom Bareń, suru sutam galaṅ hankan,~Nisira ka nam ॥koṅ॥
44~Jeṭesingi seṭerlena,~Koto koto baha lena jenga Juḍi bah ॥koṅ॥ Dhuḱ si0॥~Ji, ge, soṛanago metam,~Mutut́ mutut́ ji, ge, lalaco ॥koṅ॥siḱ du0॥
45~Ṉengań nhapuiṅ tae kena,~Gete gete Seneor tala riliṅ ha ॥koṅ॥~Ṉengań nhapuiṅ baṅ kiha,~Gete gete seneor tisaratuḍiń ॥koṅ॥

46~Gaḍako nasi ludam baha,~Ciminete Misiń koben jagaray ha ॥koṅ॥~Gutui ācim galańa,~Ciminete Misiń koben kajiāya ha ॥koṅ॥~Jahogeh metam jahogeh,~Niju seno ha ॥koṅ॥~Jahogeh metam jahogeh,~Jagaratũi ha ॥koṅ॥~Kajinatũi ha ॥koṅ॥²
47~Ṉengań Ṉapuń taekena,~Bir daru lekań goḍhanakana ॥koṅ॥~Ṉengań Ṉapuń bangaya,~Mat́ buru mat́ sakam lekań batariānah ॥koṅ॥
48~Ḍinḍa redom jarama redom, Ṉhapanum,~Boṛo redo Ṉhapanum sunum jorotan ॥koṅ॥~Non nanam, noponanam,~Boṛo redo Ṉhapanum tuḍunko tuka tan ॥koṅ॥
49~Tatań tekiṅ, Jiań tekiṅ,~Cuḍhukiṅ bonga tan goṛe, Sasaṅ banoḱa ॥koṅ॥~Sasang nakiṅ namean, buluṅ nakiṅ namean,~Cuṭu nagoy nirihan,~Nuḍũi boleahan ॥koṅ॥
50~Nender buru reaṛi misingi jeṭe teci, lolote,~Nekelantana ॥koṅ॥~Kana nhapui jeṭe, akana nhapui lolo,~Misiṅ go, laigo renge, dah go tentaṅ teha~Nekelantana ॥koṅ॥
51~Nendor Piṛi piṛite,~Hoyo cire; Gama, dudugartana ॥koṅ॥~Kana nhapui noyo, akana nhapui Gama,~Misiṅ here horen senoḱtan, hoyo dudugar ॥koṅ॥
52~Buido senoḱtan Bareń,~Ṉuli Baha cetan aete buido senoḱtan ॥koṅ॥~Ciṭṭi kulai ben Bareń,~Ṉuli mata dipilaṅ ciṭṭi kulaiben ॥koṅ॥~Kaben ciṭṭi kulai redo Bareń,~Kuṭi Ṉuli suBareńh tol gojenah ॥koṅ॥॥²
53~Ṉale Disum dona Misiń,~Jol beṛa gea Misiń jolajagada ॥koṅ॥॥~Nape Disumdoja Misiń,~Rugut́ beṛa gea Misiń ṭekora geaha ॥koṅ॥
54~Kuda ṉikir danḍika, cilikay,~Cili biliha kaben baṅṛasi ॥koṅ॥~Daru cetan cẽṛe menaḱć, koto-kotoy,~Cal baṛana, kaben toṭiha ॥koṅ॥

55~Dah do dah do, tentaṅ hintan,~Laido, laido, rengehiṅ tan,~Cimin saning reha repeṛeh, dahado namoha ॥koṅ॥²~Dah do namohago Bareń,~Raja kore pukuri dai do namoha ॥koṅ॥~Rani kore bandelare dah do namo ha~Nihatih geh sanaṅiṅ,~Cakatiṅ geh mohanĩya,~Raja kore pukuri dah do ranjet́ jan ॥koṅ॥~Rani kore bandela dah do ranjet́ jan ॥koṅ॥~(Bareń go) cimin mate seteṅ ha dah do ranjet́ jan ॥koṅ॥~Nesai sari, bah pari, cimin mate seteńa dahado~Ranjet́ jan ॥koṅ॥

56~Cetan pukuri, latar pukari,~Pan sakamdoja bare lodobekena ॥koṅ॥~Diku non tan recam, pan dom jojoma ॥koṅ॥~Raja non tan recam, pan dom jojoma ॥koṅ॥॥~Nesai sari, bapari diku non tan recama~Pan dom jojoma ॥koṅ॥

57~Nengań, napũy, menaḱć redo,~Rumatulay, rumatulay, kaji seṭerah ॥koṅ॥~Nengań, napũy, bangaya,~Rum tulay, rumatulay, kaji banoḱa ॥koṅ॥~Rumatulay, rumatulay kaji banoḱa ॥koṅ॥~Nehasari, kenajah, baleć Bareń ॥koṅ॥~Bapari, kenajai baleć Bareń॥

58~Ṉamdoja munḍa nera,~Buru diri, noharado kam sesenah ॥koṅ॥~Saiu saga, noharado kam sesenah॥~Nengam, napum, taekena,~Buru diri noharadom nuja pacuṛa ॥koṅ॥~Saiu saga noharadom, niraja sesenah ॥koṅ॥~Nesari kena jah baleć Bareń ॥koṅ॥~Bahapari kena jah ḍula Misiń ॥koṅ॥

59~Miat́ge baleć Bareń, kinjiri raja,~Beṭa beṭa teben dira dirana ॥koṅ॥~Bheṭa kiṅ cibin, kaben beṭakiṅ ॥koṅ॥~Samaṛom ganḍu rikiṅ rakabejanah ॥koṅ॥~Nesai, sari, bahapari,~Samaṛom ganḍu rikiṅ rakabejana॥
60~Tuuṉhonko turuia-turuia,~Segaṉhonko moṛea-moṛea,~Sirmajanum Jaṅcako jomtana,~Ṉotereko le coṭe, leh coṭe॥

61~Ṉabendoja baleć Bareń,~Berbenḍoṅ ber-ber kaben nekelan ॥koṅ॥~Ṭońa tapa kel, kel,~Kaben nekelan ॥koṅ॥॥~Dolaṅ seno hago Bareń,~Dolaṅ biraḍago Bareń~Berabenḍoṅ ber ber kaben nekelan ॥koṅ॥~Ṭońa tapa kel kel kaben nekelan ॥koṅ॥

62~Banda kotem senoḱredo,~Ṉoṛaḱn kotem senoḱredo,~Salukat́ Baha Bareń, toṭaa darań ben ॥koṅ॥~Kaben toṭaa daharańado, kaben beṭa daharańado,~Munḍa ko Raca Ṉuṭar bahań,~Toṭećgosoèa ॥koṅ॥~Kolam lekan, Racare,~Ciṛa bapaḍeh ॥koṅ॥॥~Nehasari kenajah baleć Bareń ॥koṅ॥~Bahapari kenajah ḍula misĩ. ॥koṅ॥

63~Barem Raca poṛoso,~Nende sakamlena, punḍi, sakam-jana,~Sabin buginah ॥koṅ॥~Cetanete lipi, gohlet́a,~Latarete noyo, gohlet́a,~Johakan lipi, torosa, naṭa natuṛiń ॥koṅ॥~Nesai sari, bahapari.~Johakan lipi, torosa, naṭa natuṛiń ॥koṅ॥

64~Soṛopo, soṛopote,~Ranci soṛopote.~Gelabar sao, nomineko, bahaleyana ॥koṅ॥~Cinḍih koi biḍeha,~Durabin ko neleha,~Danḍa ko tamea,~Jinjirih ko noh raha.~Muka, mukateko, seṭerelenah ॥koṅ॥~Bita, bittateko, seṭerelenah॥~Mongol mundi(sihabum) sima reko seṭerelenah ॥koṅ॥~Noṛo-noṛoheko panacaket́a ॥koṅ॥~Biga bigayahako ṭakayaheket́ah ॥koṅ॥²~Nihatihaṅ geh sanaṅhi, cakatihaṅ geh mohanĩya,~Noṛo noṛo-heko, pana caket́ah ॥koṅ॥~Biga bigayahako - ṭakayaheket́ah॥

65~Bakaṛi jangi jangite,~Tiramitia Karama Kaluṭi ṉatiṅêtana ॥koṅ॥~Naloreh ciru sanḍim kece kecenah ॥koṅ॥~Tiramitia karama kaluṭi natiṅ hetana ॥koṅ॥~Nerame nelangateh, doramo dolaṅ teh, doramo saṅṛi doy,~Karama kokotet́ ॥koṅ॥~Dharama kokotet́ ॥koṅ॥

66~Nete putam ranado,~Diri rici, darureh gugucuḍũiha ॥koṅ॥~Kana nhapui, diri,~Kana nhapui daru,~Jojoko, rumbulayareh gugucuḍuṅiha ॥koṅ॥~Ṉuli ko rumbũlay reh gugucuḍũiha.~Bareń honaṅ menaḱć redo, toṭe gasar meha cahe diri putam ॥koṅ॥~Tere goso meha, cahe, daru putam ॥koṅ॥~Nehasari kena jah baleć Bareń ॥koṅ॥~Bahapari kena jah ḍula Misiń ॥koṅ॥
67~Disumedo gule, gule, rajedo mele mele,~Disum cire, Bareńom nihatiń tan ॥koṅ॥~Neṅhaṅ menaḱ reca Bareń,~Disumedo Bareń goy tinulemeha ॥koṅ॥~Napuṅ menaḱ reca Bareń,~Rajedo Bareńoy kulehemeha ॥koṅ॥

68~Baleć singi tikin yana,~Baleć Canḍuḱ ponai yana,~Nokoreićatań Siṅgbonga, seday Ṉapuń do ॥koṅ॥~Ṉokoreićatań Siṅgbonga, seday Ṉengań doh॥~Cuilah kiṅ-senoy hana, cuilabano,~Nida reha kumu rikiṅ bageh ket́ीhaṅ ha ॥koṅ॥~Bheṭa kiń gehań metam,~Tebah kiṅh, gehań metam,~Bheṭayan somayareh, seday Ṉapuń menateh tiṛiṅ sabiha ॥koṅ॥~Tebayan dipilire, seday Ṉengań menete kaḍhań sabiha koṅ॥~Nehasari kena jah baleć Misiń ॥koṅ॥~Bahapari kena jah ḍula Misiń॥
69~Baleć redo, ḍula redo, dubi kuṭi,~Jobarah leka saetem nehalaha ॥koṅ॥~Nhara yanań, daru yanań, kudako,~Ṉikiradanḍika lekam cemer-cemera ॥koṅ॥
70~Jonom ken, Ṉengado,~Jonom ken Ṉapudo,~Cimin saning, sirima sorogeriha ॥koṅ॥²~Dukureho bangaya.~Suku reho bangaya,~(Siṅgbonga)~Saro, barohay, bakaṛatana ॥koṅ॥~Kapajitana ॥koṅ॥
71~Buru Disum noṛoko,~Sarajom Baha teko baṛanakanah ॥koṅ॥~ Piṛi Disum noṛoko,~Bokom Baha tirasi bisi teko Baha naka na ॥koṅ॥
72~Hora ko natom tiril sakam,~Nindi kote bangala kote kapajitana ॥koṅ॥~Puti sakam saban koṛa, neṅnde catom saban koṛa,~Nenga, napu, kajido cuilam manatiṅ ॥koṅ॥

577~Nih cire sengel, jūlot coconaṭe,~Nih cire sangaṅyaheben nūdūbaṅy tana.~Nih cire Manḍi caṭū kobo kūṛi,~Nih cire gatĩheben jagaraṅy tana..~Nih dore sengel jūlot coconṭe,~Nih dore sangaṅyahikiṅ, kaṅy sūkū jana..~Nih dore Manḍi caṭū kobo kūṛi,~Nih dore gatĩhikiṅ kaṅy kūsi jana..

578~Burū dahado seke rolo, lal cita daina, kih linḍū~Natū tana lal cita daina॥~ Piṛi dahado seke rolo, lal cita daina, kih maramar~Būhalatana, lal cita daina..~Burū dahado, seke rolo, lal cita daina, burū linḍū natū~Tana, lal cita daina..~ Piṛi dahado, seke rolo lal cita daina, Piṛi maramar~Buhal tana lal cita daina॥~Neh leka somay reh, burū linḍū natū tana lal cita~Neh leka āsaṛ reh, Piṛi maramar būhal tana~Daina..~Lal cita daina॥

579~Nūhali ko jūmabū lare, garūṛa pūtam, gana nisir~Tay leka, garūṛa pūtama.~Nica ko jaṭa reh, dūba cẽṛe, Sirma dhoti~Dūt́ bangel, tai meh talaṅ, garūṛa pūtam,~Tay leka dūba ceṛe.~Dikū būlūṅ, torasai halaṅ garūṛa pūtama.~Dūt́ bangel, tai meh talaṅ, dūba cẽṛe,~Dikū sasaṅ to rasai halaṅ dūba cẽṛe..

580~Naher dona mai, seday dona mai, ḍaḍi dah naheraleka,~Naher dona maim bikan bokona.~Naher dona mai, seday dona mai,~Cūṛa dah cirapi leka,~Naher dona maim, jiripa jalaṅ॥~Nah dona mai, gapa dona mai, nenga seta leka~Natar dona maim jamūr jaṭū̃..~Natar dona mai, gapa dona mai, būṛi minḍi leka,~Gapa dona maim soroṅ potoṅ..

581~Jah dūmaṅ, jadūr dūmaṅ mai, nete dūmaṅ sanaṛih do..~Naer tala jadūr kūṛa doh, nete kūṛi dūnūraṅ doha..~Nete dūmaṅ sanaṛih dona mai, lūtū rohageṅ kala caba jana..~Nete kūṛi dūnūraṅ dona mai, mehaḍo geh kaṅy japit́ jana..~Kaci mairem nihatĩho ha, meḍo geh kaṅy japit́ jana~Kaci mairem cakatĩho ha, lūtūrageṅh kala caba jana..

582~Gutū reh laṭū laṭū seta, sangareko bage natūm tana ॥~Dela reh, sūm daṅṛacū, kūrū cū-rici~Poyakari ko payaratūm tana..~Sangareko, bage natūm tana, nitireko topa meha.~Poyakari ko bage natūm tana, nitireko sūme meha॥~Neh leka somay reh sangareko bage natū meha॥~Neh leka nosaṛ reh, poyakari ko payaratū meha॥

583~Kūṛi yūg jana maigo, soto yug yana,~Sūba sakamere merel jo lena..~Kūṛi yūg jana maigo, soto yug yana,~Nerel cetanerem konehan tana..~Kaci mai rem nihatiṅhoha, sūba sakamere merel jo lena..~Kaci mai rem cakatĩhoha nerel cetanerem konehan tana.~Neh leka somay reh, sūba sakamere merel joh lena..~Neh leka nasaṛ reh, neharel cetonerem konehanatana॥

584~Bihūr sekir burūraha, būrū ḍoy ḍoy ḍoy,~Bihūrotarap gem neliṅha, burū ḍoy ḍoy ḍoya..~Nacūr nacūr nara reha, nara landir bah, nacū roh gem~Cihanaṅya nara landir bah॥~Jiṛi cirem sūkū yana, burū ḍoy, ḍoy ḍoy,~Bihūroḱapr gem nehalĩha, burū ḍoy ḍoy ḍoya..~Kūṛam cirem lipir yana, nara landir bah,~Nacū roh gem cinaṅya, nara landir bah॥~Nijū rema, kam nijū ha, bihūroa gem nehaliṅha,~Burū ḍoy ḍoy, ḍoy,~Seṭer rema kam seṭe rah, nacūroh gem cihnaṅy~Nara landir bah॥

585~Bandhū guṭū rah, bandhū baber, nalo reh mai gom, tole~Gojen..~Catom ṉikiredo, gūle gūle, nalo reh maigom,~Ḍabūrah gojen..~Nengam, napūmeko, sadhū leka, nalo reh maigom,~Tole gojen..~Nūnḍim, bokomeko, saheb leka, nalo rah maigom~Ḍabūra gojen..

586~Ramatiha bah, cetan reh, rabaṭĩha, ciham,~Cūṭit́, cūṭiḍah; rabaṭihaṅ..~Jankaṛi mail cetan reh, daṅṛacū, ciham,~Reṅho ceṅho ha daṅṛacū..~Jūṛi meko seno tana, ciham, cūṭit́ cūṭiḍah rabaṭĩha~Gati meko birat́ yana, ciham, reṅho caho ha daṅṛacū..~Neh leka somay reh, ciham cūṭit́ cūṭiḍah rabaṭihaṅ..~Neh leka nosaṛ reh, ciham, reó, ceṅho, ha, daṅṛacūa..

587~Lopo ṭare coke dona mainah, neraṅy nelay meneha॥~Diri mitar reṭe kaṭakom mai, neraṅy tilay meneha॥~Tega lem lemime coke doh, neraṅy nelay meneha॥~Tahūit kaca kalaṅhime, kaṭakom do neraṅy tilay meneha॥~Somay menaḱ tenamai, neraṅy nelay meneha॥~Nosaṛ menat tena mai, neraṅy tilay meneha॥

588~Daṛarema ciga nūrū, note rema, kinkoṅ banam doṅy baṛi meha॥~Daṛa rema ciga nūrū, note rema, kiṅ, koṅ, banamatehaṅ~Saḍe nonḍokom..~Somay menateh, kiṅ, koṅ, banam doṅy baṛi meha॥~Nasaṛ menateh, kiṅ, koṅ, banam teṅh saḍe nonḍokoma..

589~Neh kūṛi, rici, moca, mocatiha, neh kūṛi, nisūy neperaṅ..~Neh kūṛi, maena, kaṭa, kaṭa tiha, neh kūṛi nisūy tepega॥~Neh kūṛi, noko reko, goṅhi reh, neh kūṛiṅ kaji neseḍeh॥~Neh kūṛi, cimay reko, calih reh, neh kūṛiṅ bakaṛa~Neseḍeha..~Neh kūṛi, būnḍū reko, goṅhi reh, neh kūṛiṅ kaji neseḍe॥~Neh kūṛi, tamaṛa reko, calih reh, neh kūṛiṅ bakaṛa~Neseḍeh॥

590~Diri, bui rūgaṛi būi, kūlay dūmaṅ rūh tana॥~Lohare bui, sokoha bui, mara sūsūnatana.~Kūlay būi, dūmaṅ rūh tana ho, diri lekan samaṛom teha..~Mara bui susūn tana ho, catom lekan pinaciteh॥~Kaci mai rem nihatĩho ha kūlay mai dūmaṅ rūhatana..~Kaci mai rem cakatĩho ha, mara mai susūn tana..~Nihatiṅ nihatiṅ, dona mai, cimin matem, nihatĩha..~Cakatiṅ cakatiṅ, dona mai, cimin matem cakatĩha..~Nihatiṅ nihatiṅ tena mai, singi jaket́ nasūr jana..~Cakatiṅ, cakatiṅ tena mai, canḍū jaket́ tala~Tikin jana..

591~Dhobi hor dhoba lija sobot́ bagetat́ teh,~Dhobi hor dhobam, boro saheṕ jana..~Nata nail, pesekar babū, ho dhorom bage tat́ teh,~Nata nail, pesekar babūm, kirisatan jana..~Kaci mairem nihatiho ho,~Dhobi hor dhoba borosaheṕ jana.~Kaci mairem, caka tiho ha,~Nata nail pesekar babū kirisatan jana.

592~Burū koyatem nelaṅ dolaṅ, liḍiṅha..~Gaṛa koyatem ṭanka, ṭore, liḍiṅha..~Neteṛem nasūliṅ leka geh, neteṛem jotonihaṅ leka,~Pati cahūli manḍim jome hana mai॥~Konca raṅbaṛa nūtūm tagoyaha.~Neteṛem, nasūliṅ leka geha..~Neteṛem, jotoniṅ leka..~Kaci mairem, nihatĩhoha, pati cahūli manḍim tagoyaha~Kaci mairem, cakatĩho ha, konca raṅbaṛa nūtūm jomeha॥.

593~Naṅy mai ḍinḍa reh, baro so. Nacanikoṅy nacabakena.~Niṅ mai ḍangūṛa reh, tero so gopinekoṅy sikabakena..~Niṅ mai nera naguhan, baro so na caniko senojana..~Niṅ mai nera naṛadihan, tero so gopineko birat́ jana..~Kaci mai rem nihatiṅ hoha.,~Baro so nacanikoyaṅ nacabakena..~Kaci mairem cakatĩho ha,~Tero so gopinekoṅy sikab kena..

594~Kita mah sagenoh, lidi lidi, pogomah jaṛa,~Pogomah jaṛa doṅy beṭaliha॥~Barū mah sagenoh, lidi lidi, baromaciti,~Baromaciti doṅy tebatar liha..~Hori honatoro, jonate kailoṅy men liha, pogomah~Jaṛa pogomah jaṛa, doy, koko doro haṅya॥~Sapa sih kenatero, bis melaṅy, menaliha,~Baromah citi, baromah citi doy biṅhaḍū jana..

598~Nire nire mego maigo, sene sene megoh~Ḍeṅḱapar, ḍeṅḱar, burū doko sangar tana..~Nire nire mego maigo, sene sene megoh,~Pole pole ṉikir doko neloyatana..~Ḍeṅa ḍeṅḱap, burū doko, sangar tana,~Nire nire mehaleh kulay cūṛūṅ cūḍū̃..~Pole pole ṉikir doko, nehaloy tana,~Nire nire mehaleh horo lipa laṛe॥~Kaci mairem nihatihoha,~Nire nire mahale kūlay cūṛūṅ cūḍū̃.॥.~Kaci mairem cakatĩho ha,~Nire nire mehale horolipa laṛe.

599~Nih cire dada, bilay met́ menḍe hoṅ, nih cire~Dadam nudūbaṅy tana.~Nih cire dada, sūkari moca lamar lumūr,~Nih cire dadam jagaraṅy tana.~Nihaha tam dada, bilay met́ meḍehoṅ,~Nihaha tam daday lūnḍū lūnḍūhayaṅ.~Nihaha tam dada, sūkari moca lamar lumūr~Nihaha tam daday rese rese haṅyaha॥~Nihaha tam dada, gihūa cigo banū taja,~Nihaha tam daday lanḍū lūnḍū hayaṅ.~Nihaha tam dada saram cigo banū taja,~Nihaha tam daday rese resehaṅya..

623~Ne dumaṅṅ g juṛi dumaṅng~Ne dumang sanaṛi do,~Nen kuṛi kin juṛi kuṛi king~Nen kuṛi kin duraṅṅ g do.~Nen dumaṅng sanaṛi do~Senoge sanaṅnga.~Nen kuṛi kin dunuraṅng do~Birat́ ge moninga.~Seno redo kacime senotar~Seno gem kajia.~Birat́ redo kacime biraḍa~Birat́ gem bakaṛa.~Nam bole senoare~Paiki baṅy Baha joma.~Nam bole biraḍare~Naṭal bahaeṅ ḍali joma.~Paiki baeṅ Baha tare~Say sayatem nelinga.~Naṭal Baha ḍali tare~Moco moco landa yena.

919~Noyaṅr meko sunum maire nanar meko sasaṅ,~Noyar meko sunum maire nanar meko sasaṅ.~Gitil teko misa taṛa gitil segoy maire gitil~Segoy segoy mai re॥~Neaṅ noṛa sunum maire napaṅ noṛa sasaṅ,~Neaṅ noṛa sunum maire napa noṛa sasaṅ.~Meti teko misa tat́a meti modaṅl modaṅla maire meti~Modaṅl modaṅla maire॥
920~Būrū kocare Gama lere.~Latar āṛi ko jaket́ rapūḍalena.~Latar āṛi ko jaket́ rapūt́ lena.~Casi hoṛo ko ena ko nel kan meḍada ko joro.
921~Saning disum babū sage bariya.~Canda ṭaka babū nalom nataṅ.~Candan ṭaka babū nalom nataṅ.~Nama korom babū nama kopaṛa.~Tisiṅ dore babū seṭer rakana.
922~EEE
923~Gae seṭer gae toli.~Kaṛa seṭer kaṛa toli.~Kaṛa tole tala nida.~Cet́ baba go segeḍi tana.
924~Tara baman haṭi tara mogal mondi do sima ḍule ket́~Tol ket́ cando leka.~Ḍule ket́ tol ket́ cando leka.
925~Kaṭi cora dokaba toṛa roṛayalaṅ pūloḍabayalaṅ.~Nidihalaṅ pūlo kotaṛahaṭate.~Keja halaṅ pūlo naki narasi.
626~Nat geca nah būi, būi, ko meta meha.~Natar geca nah mai, mai mai ko metameha॥~Daṛi dat rena mai, cūṛa daa rena mai,~Jal meha koh, caṭoṕ meha koh॥.
927~Dumbi sai natu kuṭi rena;~Sengel Gamay Gama let́a,~Pali jeṭe, jeṭe let́a,~Nalo mai, nam, nudūbeha,~Masūri ben nereteha..~Kalay ben nereteha..

928~Manḍi mai nay, bukū redo,~Nili mai nay noyol redo,~Koālū rehanah sa akante,~Tega laṅbe ḍai menaḱ būi naha..~Tega lebe ḍai menaḱ būi naha..~Noṛayate kulū sūi meh, duār rekay baṭi hota..~Duārete kulūsūi meh, Raca rekay tipi hota..
929~Cimin saning rema nah, taṭi murūham, taṭi murūham..~Buijah seṭerehana, singi nasūrehanaha..~Taṭi murūham, taṭi surūham..

930~Nengam noṛa Sasaṅ mai reh, napūm noṛa sunūm,~Niti teko misataḍa, niti mutūt́ mutūt́, niti mutūt́ mutūt́॥~Hanar meko noṛa Sasaṅ mai reh hoyaraṅ meko sunūm~Gitilako misa tat́a,~Gitil segoy, segoy, gitil segoy, segoya..
931~Kaṭay tem nehalĩha Sirma jakem nehalĩha,~Siṅbiṛi sakam lab labo,~Siṅbiṛi sakam labo labo..~Mihaḍege, ṕ/retĩh, cimin mateṅ singaren,~Siṅbiṛi sakam lab labo..~Siṅbiṛi sakam lab labo..

932~Lai doh, lai do renge hiṅ tan.~Dat doh, dat do tetaṅhiṅ tan, tetaṅhiṅ tana..~Boyana goṛeṅ nijūlen, sinkū ko disūmate..~Sinkū ko disūmate॥~Dokaṅy goṛe rūhaha, bhagabila, toro teh~Bhagabila, toro, hatū jagadah reh birūā koh~Disūm reh, joben joben sanaṅhiṅ tana..~Joben joben sanaṅhintana..

633~Cih, cih menatem kehaliḍing, kūla hab doha.~Tagoy doha..~Rocot́ doha..~Ili taṅy jojo tan, cauli taṅy rela tan,~Menate gedam, keha āgu liḍiṅha, kūla habadoh~Tagoy doh, rocot́ doha..~Sūkūri jome lūpū tem, lobo lobo liḍiṅha,~Sim ḍaḍe kudi tem, ti titi liḍiṅha,~Kula hab doh, tagoy toh, rocot́ doha..~Kūla burū piṭū āt koṅe namanate,~Pumpū lai jojo āt koeṅ namanateh,~Keha āguli ḍiṅhay, kula hab doh,~Tagoy doh, rocot́ doha..~Menat menaredo lola, menat metaṅy meh,~Bano menaredo lola, bano metaṅy meh,~Pūti sakam sab kete, ramo ramo leh paṛaorameha..~Ramo ramo leh paṛao meha॥
934~Kūṭi kūṭi teh, maci maci teh,~Sengel siṅh doṅy roṛa let́a,~Sengel siṅh doṅy roṛa let́a~Tare nare teh, nare nare teh,~Niraja bolo. Lena jam ḍokora,~Niraja bolo lena jam ḍokorah॥.
935~Nape tape do mai tape doh-kaka sakam,~Tiṅbhar boṅोr, tiṅbhar boṅbhor, mai tape doha..~Mai tape doha..~Nale tale do boyo tale doh, mapa sadom lekay,~Dhingar dhongor, boyo tale do boyo tale doh॥.
